  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb3\u0bcd !",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "There should be room for discussion in the Parliament regarding the attack on Khalimugatidal - Kiriella's request!",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Prime Minister of the Opposition, Korada Laxman Kiriella, said that we are demanding that there be room for a debate on the upcoming 27th in the Parliament regarding the attack on the Khalimugatidal protestors.",
        "Opposition Prime Minister Korda has requested the Prime Minister and the Speaker to convene Parliament tomorrow to discuss the attack on Khalimugatdal protesters.",
        "The government had attacked the protestors who were engaged in a peaceful protest in Kalimugat last Friday night in a very brutal manner. We have requested the Prime Minister and the Speaker to convene the Parliament on the 25th tomorrow to hold a discussion in this regard.",
        "However, as it is difficult to convene the parliament tomorrow and to call the members of parliament amid the fuel issue, we request the government to take up this discussion when the parliament meets on Wednesday 27th to approve the regular gazette notification.",
        "It is illegal and anti-democratic to attack and chase the protestors who were protesting peacefully. Therefore, it is necessary to establish a concept in this regard, he said."
      ],
